A vast crystalline network of interconnected translucent spheres floating in deep space, each sphere containing miniature glowing cityscapes in different colors - some amber, some teal, some violet. Delicate bridges of light connect certain spheres to each other while others remain isolated. The spheres closest to the viewer are larger and more detailed, showing tiny buildings and pathways within, while distant spheres fade into a soft nebula of purple and blue gas clouds. The composition suggests hierarchy and selective connection, with three distinct clusters of spheres at different elevations, each cluster having its own dominant color temperature. Studio Ghibli style with soft cel-shading, dreamlike atmosphere, gentle gradients, and that characteristic sense of wonder and scale found in Miyazaki's floating castle scenes.
